  "_comment": "Cinema Worldbuilder hi-res t2v on LTX 2.3 22B DEV-FP8 + DISTILL LORA. Built from the Comfy-Org template (video_ltx2_3_t2v.json) with: (a) DualCLIPLoaderGGUF substituted for LTXAVTextEncoderLoader since gemma_3_12B_it_fp4_mixed.safetensors is not on disk and the GGUF gemma is proven; (b) Cinema Worldbuilder nodes (CameraBlock + AudioLine + PromptComposer) wired into the positive CLIPTextEncode to drive the prompt with the v2 grammar. Requires: ltx-2.3-22b-dev-fp8.safetensors (checkpoints/), ltxv/ltx2/ltx-2.3-22b-distilled-lora-384-1.1.safetensors (loras/), ltx-2.3-spatial-upscaler-x2-1.1.safetensors (latent_upscale_models/), gemma-3-12b-it-IQ4_XS.gguf + ltx-2.3_text_projection_bf16.safetensors (text_encoders/). Verified working on ComfyUI 0.16.4, RTX 4070 Ti 12 GB. ~290 sec wall for a 1280x704 5-sec clip with audio."
